profile: Langley Excavation and Drainage serves Langley, Fort Langley, Aldergrove, Surrey, Abbotsford, Chilliwack and surrounding areas. Built upon a solid bedrock of 20+ years experience in a combination of  commercial and residential, Langley Excavation and Drainage provides: driveway replacement, fence building, deck building, excavation and drainage installation; service line trenching and installation; landscaping; sod installation; demolition; debris removal; power washing; exterior carpentry: deck construction; fence construction; wooden stair construction; concrete work and snow removal. Langley Excavation and Drainage offers you professional, courteous, timely commercial and residential services

This care is represented by our amazing team, our designs as well as our outstanding landscapes. Quality comes second nature to us, as the belief in providing our clients with a landscape to out preform, out last and out do always shines through.  
We love meeting new people who want to renovate their yard, turn it into a oasis and use the amazing team at Jovak. 
Contact us today for a free consult to start the process!
